(Could someone please do something to Vulois. I don't want him to sit 
there.)

Gotron

Gotron got alarmed as the holographic image popped out of the probe.

"What kind of creature is that?"
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream saw that the Lavacons were bored. He sent a message to 
Phobia.

"Phobia, it's Starscream. I'm at the Pred cave with the re-
inforcements They are restless and won't wait long. You have to get 
here, NOW!"
______________________________________________________________________
Brix/Fliq

Brix and Fliq patted Koj and Inu-Yashu on the back.

"Alright! Even more bots to save Striker and Spears!"

They continued their walk with the others.
______________________________________________________________________
Trainers

Prebon shook his head.

"No, I could not do that. I can't put another spark away for all this 
time just to bring him out. You might be in there for centuries. And 
if all goes well with Ramulus, he won't have to wait much longer 
Besides," Prebon said while checking out Spears' feminine 
physique, "I don't think he would feel comfortable in your body."

Meanwhile, the other were in position. Ignatius spoke up.

"If were in cloak, how come were so far away from the exchange zone?"

"Because," answered Hammer, "When we were at The Ark we saw a cat-
like bot. She can probably smell very good. She would pick us up. 
This way she can't smell us, were within comm range and we can be at 
the battle sight in just under 3 minutes!"
